  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You linger forever in the minds of those you’ve haunted. You can now use <strong>Miss Me?</strong> targeting anyone or anything you’ve previously targeted with one of your Absence abilities, regardless of where either of you are before you roll. If you do, roll [quality] instead of Persistence.</p><p>If you fail a roll while using Bogeyman's effect, the target becomes immune to your Absence powers forever – and to your perception. They will always be a gap in your senses. You will never know they’re coming.</p>",
